		"description": {
			"value": "<p>You create a Pact Tome to contain more spells.</p><ul><li><p>When you gain this feature, choose three cantrips from any class's spell list. The cantrips you choose can be from different classes. While the Pact Tome is on your person, you can cast those cantrips at will as if they were warlock spells. These cantrips don't count against your number of cantrips known.</p></li><li><p>If you lose your Pact Tome, you can perform a 1-hour ceremony to create a replacement. This ceremony can be performed during a short or long rest, and it destroys the previous tome. The tome turns to ash when you die.</p></li></ul>",
